Class FilterCriteriaDTO

java.lang.Object
org.osgi.dto.DTO
org.osgi.service.onem2m.dto.FilterCriteriaDTO
public class FilterCriteriaDTO extends DTO
DTO expresses FilterCriteria. This data structure is used for searching resources.
